  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 1,800 students get quality teachers in Kenya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education is the surest path to prosperity, and teachers play a vital role in a child&apos;s education. Yet in Kenya&apos;s primary schools, the ratio of students to teachers is 47:1. When teachers are in charge of so many children, students&apos; education can suffer. By supporting teachers, Hope 4 Africa&apos;s partner schools can hire more qualified teachers and ensure they have the tools they need to provide a quality education to students. Help Hope 4 Africa sponsor 3 teachers at 6 schools with this project.</narrative>
  </description>
